---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Insights — Forge T Labs"
  description="Articles and insights on Microsoft Dynamics 365, Azure, AI and the Microsoft Cloud for real estate and construction."
  canonical="https://forgetlabs.com/insights"
  ogType="website"
  active="Insights"
>
<main id="top">
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="hero-glow"></div>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="crumb"><a href="/">Home</a> &nbsp;/&nbsp; Insights</div>
    <h1>Insights on the <em>Microsoft Cloud</em>.</h1>
    <p class="lede">Practical answers on Dynamics 365, Azure, AI and Modern Work &mdash; written
      for the teams making real decisions about their Microsoft platform.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-head reveal">
      <span class="mono">Latest</span>
      <h2>Articles &amp; <em>guidance</em>.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="ind-grid">
      <a href="/dynamics-365-for-construction" class="ind reveal" style="display:block">
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3fc878" stroke-width="1.6">
          <path d="M3 21h18M6 21V8l6-4 6 4v13"/><path d="M10 21v-5h4v5" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Dynamics 365 for construction firms</h3>
        <p>What Dynamics 365 actually offers commercial contractors &mdash; and where it fits in
          a construction business.</p>
        <span class="tag">Dynamics 365</span>
      </a>
      <div class="ind reveal" style="opacity:.55">
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3fc878" stroke-width="1.6">
          <path d="M12 3v6m0 6v6M3 12h6m6 0h6" stroke-linecap="round"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/></svg></div>
        <h3>More articles coming soon</h3>
        <p>We are building out a library of practical guidance on AI, Azure and the Microsoft
          Cloud. Check back, or subscribe via our contact page.</p>
        <span class="tag">In progress</span>
      </div>
      <div class="ind reveal" style="opacity:.55">
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3fc878" stroke-width="1.6">
          <rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M3 9h18M8 18v3M16 18v3" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Want the full guide?</h3>
        <p>Our downloadable guide, "Dynamics 365 for Construction," goes deeper than any single
          article. Get it from our resources page.</p>
        <span class="tag">Resource</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section style="padding-top:40px">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="cta-band reveal">
      <div class="glow"></div>
      <h2>Get the construction guide.</h2>
      <p>Our free guide goes deeper than the articles &mdash; the full picture of Dynamics 365
        for commercial contractors.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/resources">Get the free guide &rarr;</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/contact">Talk to us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</main>
</BaseLayout>
